name: fBEETS Staking
description: Supplies fBEETS to BeethovenX for BEETS rewards. Rewards are harvested and staked into BEETS-WFTM pool for more fBEETS for the strategy. In addition, the deposited fBEETS are periodically used for gauge voting to boost all BeethovenX stable pools that Yearn invests in.
